reviewText: Really old footage. More about Sea World, etc... than wild Orcas. Still not a bad documentary

An absolutely wonderful tale of the wolves of the sea.  They also travel in packs called pods and are loving to their family and are the smarted mammals on earth.  I was kissed by Corky at Marineland, the most wonderful experience on earth.  She is shown in this film.  This film shows the discovery of Mamu, the first whale in captivity and started the love and understanding of these beautiful creatures.  A most watch for whale lovers and a lesson to those why aren't.
My 3yr old Grandson loves this series. He is a Shark and Shamu fan! So glad I purchased this! Thank you
If you have not had a chance to view some books for beginners interested in wildlife, these are good books to give as gifts.
This DVD was a gift for my daughter-in-law. She loved it, very informative abouth the story of the Orca. It is a short documentary. Great shots of the orcas.
very educating. I never know that Orca is very fascinating. I learn so much about them. Please transfer all the other episode to dvd.
